<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_305" id="151v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"/>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_305_r2l14">Wır ~ dıe <expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> etc Bekennen etc / Von der nom <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_305_r2l15"><expan>gnedıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>cʒog</expan> Johannſen von Peyern dıener vnd dıe dabey </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_305_r2l16"><expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ſınd . etwıeuıl <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>b<ex>urgern</ex></expan> vnd ıren armen <expan>leẅte<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒu feẅcht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_305_r2l17">getan <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> / Darumb ein teydıng getroffen ıſt als vns dıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_305_r2l18"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> geſagt vnd gebetten <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> freẅnd <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ʒu <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_305_r2l19">Alſo <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> wır <expan>all<ex>er</ex></expan> der dıe <expan>darunt<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dacht</expan> ſınd gut freẅnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_305_r2l20">vmb dıe tat on <expan>geu<ex>er</ex>de</expan> Mıt <expan>vrk<ex>unde</ex></expan> / <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſıgelt</expan> mıt <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_305_r2l21"><expan>aufgedrukt<ex>en</ex></expan> Jnſıgel . <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ıııȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> marıe magdalene </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_305" id="151v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab/></div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Wir, die <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> etc., bekennen etc. von der nom
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan> Johannsen von Peyern diener und die dabey
                                <expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan> sind etwievil
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgern</ex></expan> und iren armen
                            <expan>lewte<ex>n</ex></expan> zu Fewcht getan
                            <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, darumb ein teyding getroffen ist, als uns
                        die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> gesagt und gebetten
                            <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> frewnd <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> zu
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>. Also <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>
                        wir <expan>all<ex>er</ex></expan> der, die <expan>darunt<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>dacht</expan> sind, gut frewnd umb die tat on
                                <expan>gev<ex>er</ex>de</expan>. Mit <expan>urk<ex>unde</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>sigelt</expan> mit <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>aufgedrukt<ex>en</ex></expan> insigel. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iiii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Marie Magdalene.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
